name: Alicia Silverstone
description:
Alicia Silverstone

Actress and mother Alicia Silverstone was in the move Clueless and some music video things back in the 90s I believe.

This is the LoRA counterpart to my embedding.

The results, as they say, speak for themselves

This works best on 0.6-0.8 strength and the consistent-Factor model.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

(all images used to train this model are of Ms. Silverstone 18-years old and older)
